<style>
  /* Requisito: Cambiar la fuente en toda la página */
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
  }
  
  /* cambiar color, fondo y bordes*/
  .seccion-conocerte {
    background-color: #f8f9fa; 
    color: #212529; 
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 2px solid #0d6efd; 
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  /* Clases para que el Modo Oscuro funcione */
  .modo-oscuro {
    background-color: #121212;
    color: #e0e0e0;
  }
  .modo-oscuro .seccion-conocerte {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    border-color: #0dcaf0;
  }
  
  /* 1. El cuerpo de la tabla (lo clarito) pasa a ser oscuro */
  .modo-oscuro .table, .modo-oscuro .table td {
    background-color: #212529 !important; 
    color: #e0e0e0 !important;
    border-color: #444 !important;
  }
  
  /* 2. El encabezado de la tabla (lo oscuro) pasa a ser clarito */
  .modo-oscuro .table-dark th {
    background-color: #f8f9fa !important;
    color: #212529 !important;
    border-color: #ddd !important;
  }
</style>

<div class="bg-primary text-white p-3 shadow-sm mb-4">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <h1 class="mb-0">Gonzalo's Website!!</h1>
    <button class="btn btn-dark text-light font-weight-bold" onclick="cambiarTema()">☀️/🌙 Change Theme</button>
  </div>  
</div>

<div class="container">
  <p>Hello everyone, my name is Gonzalo!. I am a Civil Engineering student from the "Universidad de Los Andes" in Chile!, I entered in 2020 and im currently in my 10th semester, so im near finishing my degree.
    Now im going to tell you a little about me. I love playing video games. It doesn't matter the genre, i just love playing them, and i also love watching movies and series, my favourite series is "Naruto and Naruto Shippuden", also a fun fact i played league of legends from its beginning and i reached my top rank at diamond league!
  </p>     
  
  <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <p>If you dont know who Naruto is, here you have an image of him! </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2">
      <%= image_tag "NarutoImage.jpg", class: "img-fluid rounded w-75", alt: "Naruto" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <p>Also this is my GitHub Profile:
        <a class="link-primary" href="https://github.com/Gonzan1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          https://github.com/Gonzan1
        </a>
      </p>
      <p> My skills at the moment are:</p>
      <table class="table table-light table-bordered">
        <thead>
          <tr class="table-dark">
            <th scope="col">Skill</th>
            <th scope="col">Level</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Python</td>
            <td>Intermediate</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Excel</td>
            <td>Advanced</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>PostgreSQL</td>
            <td>Basic</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>English</td>
            <td>Advanced</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Spanish</td>
            <td>Native</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="seccion-conocerte">
    <h3>Now i want to know you...</h3>
    <p>I already told you a little about me. What do you like to do?</p>
    
    <div class="input-group mb-3">
      <input type="text" id="inputHobby" class="form-control" placeholder="Ex: reading, going to the gym, etc..." aria-label="Hobby">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" onclick="mostrarHobby()">Send</button>
    </div>

    <h4 id="resultadoHobby" class="mt-3 text-info"></h4>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function cambiarTema() {
    document.body.classList.toggle("modo-oscuro");
  }

  function mostrarHobby() {
    let hobby = document.getElementById("inputHobby").value;
    document.getElementById("resultadoHobby").innerText = "¡Nice! So you like: " + hobby + ". ¡Thanks for sharing!";
  }
</script>